<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 07:34:36 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>空军新型 VC-25B“桥”喷气机已加入总统空运大队（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/new-air-force-vc-25b-bridge-jet-has-joined-the-presidential-airlift-group</link><description>&lt;p&gt;新型空军一号喷气式飞机将在搭载唐纳德·特朗普总统之前进行最后一轮测试。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/new-air-force-vc-25b-bridge-jet-has-joined-the-presidential-airlift-group"&gt;新型空军 VC-25B“桥”喷气机已加入总统空运大队（更新）&lt;/a&gt;后首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2026 21:27:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/new-air-force-vc-25b-bridge-jet-has-joined-the-presidential-airlift-group</guid></item><item><title>地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-196</link><description>&lt;p&gt;天啊……PlayStation 刚刚坏了。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-196"&gt;《地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情》&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2026 20:41:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-196</guid></item><item><title>RC-135 铆钉接头可控制无人机，大幅扩展收集能力</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/rc-135-rivet-joints-could-control-drones-to-drastically-expand-collection-capabilities</link><description>&lt;p&gt;与无人机合作可能为铆钉接头带来新的运营可能性，其他发展也即将到来。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/rc-135-rivet-joints-could-control-drones-to-drastically-expand-collection-capabilities"&gt;RC-135 铆钉接头可以控制无人机，大幅扩展收集能力&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2026 18:51:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/rc-135-rivet-joints-could-control-drones-to-drastically-expand-collection-capabilities</guid></item><item><title>陆军最新部队旨在在太平洋战斗中用无人机“压倒”对手</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/armys-newest-unit-wants-to-overwhelm-adversaries-with-drones-in-pacific-fight</link><description>&lt;p&gt;新的第七步兵师太平洋多域司令部将把无人机战与史赛克旅的机动能力融为一体。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/armys-newest-unit-wants-to-overwhelm-adversaries-with-drones-in-pacific-fight"&gt;陆军最新部队旨在在太平洋战斗中用无人机“压倒”对手，&lt;/a&gt;该部队首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2026 17:55:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/armys-newest-unit-wants-to-overwhelm-adversaries-with-drones-in-pacific-fight</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯“天幕杀机”核动力巡航导弹的实际工作原理如下</title><link>https://www.twz.com/nuclear/here-how-russias-skyfall-nuclear-powered-cruise-missile-actually-works</link><description>&lt;p&gt;研究人员得出的结论是，核动力巡航导弹几乎肯定使用直接循环发动机，在整个飞行过程中喷出放射性物质。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/nuclear/here-how-russias-skyfall-nuclear-powered-cruise-missile-actually-works"&gt;俄罗斯“天幕杀机”核动力巡航导弹的实际工作原理是这样的，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2026 16:11:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/nuclear/here-how-russias-skyfall-nuclear-powered-cruise-missile-actually-works</guid></item><item><title>莫斯科遭受乌克兰猛烈空袭的非凡镜头</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/extraordinary-footage-from-moscow-under-heavy-ukrainian-aerial-attack</link><description>&lt;p&gt;乌克兰对莫斯科的大规模打击引发大规模爆炸和火灾，可能预示着远程空战进入了新阶段。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/extraordinary-footage-from-moscow-under-heavy-ukrainian-aerial-attack"&gt;莫斯科遭受乌克兰猛烈空袭的非凡镜头&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 21:55:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/extraordinary-footage-from-moscow-under-heavy-ukrainian-aerial-attack</guid></item><item><title>HH-60W 直升机变成 VIP 运输机，国会质疑空军的战斗救援准备情况</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/congress-questions-air-forces-combat-rescue-readiness-as-hh-60w-helicopters-get-turned-into-vip-transports</link><description>&lt;p&gt;显然，HH-60W 机队并不适合太平洋地区，但人们对专用战斗救援能力的担忧与日俱增。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/congress-questions-air-forces-combat-rescue-readiness-as-hh-60w-helicopters-get-turned-into-vip-transports"&gt;国会质疑 HH-60W 直升机变成 VIP 运输机后空军的战斗救援准备情况&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 20:11:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/congress-questions-air-forces-combat-rescue-readiness-as-hh-60w-helicopters-get-turned-into-vip-transports</guid></item><item><title>不，一架 VC-25A 空军一号喷气式飞机尚未退役</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/no-the-air-force-isnt-retiring-a-vc-25a-air-force-one-jet-just-yet</link><description>&lt;p&gt;前卡塔尔 VC-25B“桥”飞机即将投入使用，但与报道相反，较旧的 VC-25A 将继续飞行。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;帖子&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/no-the-air-force-isnt-retiring-a-vc-25a-air-force-one-jet-just-yet"&gt;“不，一架 VC-25A 空军一号喷气机尚未退役”&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 18:40:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/no-the-air-force-isnt-retiring-a-vc-25a-air-force-one-jet-just-yet</guid></item><item><title>海军最终寻求处置世界上第一艘核动力巡洋舰长滩号</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-finally-seeking-to-dispose-of-uss-long-beach-the-worlds-first-nuclear-powered-cruiser</link><description>&lt;p&gt;拆解一艘核动力战舰比传统动力战舰的成本和时间都要高得多。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-finally-seeking-to-dispose-of-uss-long-beach-the-worlds-first-nuclear-powered-cruiser"&gt;海军最终寻求处置世界上第一艘核动力巡洋舰长滩号&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 17:39:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/navy-finally-seeking-to-dispose-of-uss-long-beach-the-worlds-first-nuclear-powered-cruiser</guid></item><item><title>MQ-9 获得机载预警雷达意义重大</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/mq-9-getting-airborne-early-warning-radar-is-a-huge-deal</link><description>&lt;p&gt;搭载雷达吊舱的 MQ-9 提供了一种经济且高度灵活的持久机载预警解决方案，现在比以往任何时候都更需要这种解决方案。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/mq-9-getting-airborne-early-warning-radar-is-a-huge-deal"&gt;MQ-9 获得机载预警雷达是一件大事，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 17:03:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/mq-9-getting-airborne-early-warning-radar-is-a-huge-deal</guid></item></channel></rss>